# HabitByHabit

**Build better habits, one day at a time.**

A minimalist iOS app that helps you focus on building one habit at a time. Track your daily streak, receive personalized reminders, and stay motivated with daily quotes.

## Features

- ✅ **Single Habit Focus**: Build one habit at a time for maximum effectiveness
- ✅ **Streak Tracking**: Watch your streak grow as you complete your habit daily
- ✅ **Daily Reminders**: Get notified at your preferred time to never miss a day
- ✅ **Calendar Integration**: Sync your habits to your calendar (Premium)
- ✅ **Advanced Analytics**: Track your progress with detailed insights (Premium)
- ✅ **Multiple Habits**: Manage up to 3 habits simultaneously (Premium)
- ✅ **Motivational Quotes**: Start each day with an inspiring quote

